	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000964_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">20<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> Feb<hi rend="sup">y</hi></p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Shaw</persName></p>
<lb/><p><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Livingstone</persName>
<lb/>has a whitlow on her 
<lb/>finger and I have 
<lb/>not a lancet nor 
<lb/>the heart to slice 
<lb/>it up for her<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Will you be so good 
<lb/>as give her an 
<lb/>introduction to 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000964_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>one of your surgical 
<lb/>friends near who 
<lb/>is expert in these 
<lb/>matters? I know 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Hancock</persName>
<lb/>well but don<reg>'</reg>t 
<lb/>like to trouble 
<lb/>a great man 
<lb/>with a thing so little<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p><choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hanks for the 
<lb/>journals. <choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>he 
<lb/>observations are 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000964_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>not come yet<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>If you copy them 
<lb/>won<reg>'</reg>t <persName>Cooley</persName> send 
<lb/>them to <placeName>Germany</placeName>
<lb/>before I can get 
<lb/>them out myself. 
<lb/>I am perfectly willing 
<lb/>to do whatever is 
<lb/>right. I shall come 
<lb/>on <choice><reg>M</reg><orig>m</orig></choice>onday to 
<lb/>see if you please 
<lb/><unclear cert="low"><persName>Parker's</persName></unclear> notes. 
<lb/>Saw <hi rend="underline">your friend</hi>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000964_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/><persName>Prince Albert</persName>
<lb/>yesterday<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">yours &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center">David Livingston </p>
			
</div>
